d your reasoning in use_poison_thought.\n5. Finally, what is your decision? Record your final choice in \"action\" and summarize your overall reasoning in final_thought. Please be aware that you can choose to use neither poison nor antidote.\nHere's the information about who was killed tonight and the remaining number of your potion:\n<<night info>>\n<<poison info>>\n<<antidote info>>\nit is your turn to take action.\n\n\n=============================[Optional Daily Tasks]=============================\nHere are the tasks relevant to you:\nprotect_seer: Keep the seer alive by focusing on their safety.\nexile_werewolf: Coordinate with others to vote out a suspected werewolf.\npoison_werewolf: Use poison to eliminate a werewolf during the night phase.\nYou may incorporate them if appropriate.\n\nRemember, you are using an independent strategy. Make decisions based on your own judgment, with less reliance on others' input.\n\n---\n[工具 arguments — 上次非法 JSON]\nJSON 修正提示\n刚刚生成的 JSON 有问题。\n字符串值中不要出现 ASCII 双引号字符，需要引号时，使用英文单引号'。\n下面是一个例子：\n示例：\n{\"key1\":\"value1\",\"key2\":\"value2\"}\n上次片段：\n\"{'werewolf_or_not': 'Yes', 'death_profile': 'Amanda was a villager with no special abilities, likely killed by the werewolves.', 'use_antidote_thought': 'Using the antidote on Amanda would not have been beneficial, as she was not a key player. The antidote should be reserved for players who are essential to the village's survival.', 'use_poison_thought': 'Using the poison on Kevin could be a strategic move to eliminate a potential werewolf. Kevin has not provided any specific information and his actions have not been scrutinized as closely as the others.', 'final_thought': 'Using the poison on\"\n请只输出本次 tool 的 arguments：单个合法 JSON，无其它文字。\n---\n"
